headline: Carnival Corporation & plc (CCL): A Bull Case Theory
summary: We came across a bullish thesis on Carnival Corporation & plc (NYSE:CCL) on Substack by Alpha Ark Team. In this article, we will summarize the bulls’ thesis on CCL. Carnival Corporation & plc (NYSE:CCL)’s share was trading at $25.66 as of Dec 26th. CCL’s trailing and forward P/E were 17.82 and 14.68 respectively according to Yahoo Finance. […]

headline: One Growth Stock Down 64% to Buy Right Now
summary: The performance of Carnival Corp (NYSE: CCL) has likely frustrated its long-term investors over the last few years.  The company reported revenue of $25 billion in fiscal 2024, a yearly improvement of 16%.
